    <summary>Program to automatically switch between different keyboard layouts</summary>
    <releaseNotes>#### What's new in this version 4.4:
1. Diary
    * Added one more item of settings, allowing you to enable or disable saving data from the clipboard in exception programs
    * Stabilized the work of the Diary
    * We returned the ability to put the password on the diary and work with it correctly
1. Social networks
    Now you can share the experience of using Punto through Google+ and Odnoklassniki
1. Exception Programs
    Improved the addition of the program by title
1. MS Office
    Improved work with Office2013 and Office2016 on Win7x32
1. Fixed floating indicator
    Now it disappears itself, a few seconds after the end of the input, if the corresponding setting is enabled
1. Hotkeys
    Removed hot keys using the Win button (due to Win10 upgrade to 1709)
1. Updated the program help
1. We fixed compatibility with rare but important programs (GitGUI, Atom)
    </releaseNotes>
